# XFlickr Crawler — repository quality foundation

Read `AGENTS.md` before non-trivial work.

- Package: `jooservices/xflickr-crawler`
- Quality gate: `composer check` (local), `composer ci` (coverage)
- Pint wins formatting conflicts; PHPCS is structural only
- Crawl entry: `FlickrService::connection()` only
- No OAuth in package; app credentials in laravel-config `xflickr_app.{profile}`
- One queued job per Flickr API page
- Git flow: dto standard (`develop` integration, `release/<version>` → `master`)
- Stop and ask when requirements conflict with source truth
- Canonical skills: `.github/skills/`
